{
  "title": "Garlicky Chewy Energizing Mediterranean Butter Beans Stir-fry",
  "description": "A quick and easy Mediterranean-inspired dish featuring butter beans, garlic, and other fresh vegetables for a flavorful, raw-friendly breakfast or snack.",
  "cuisine": "Mediterranean",
  "diet": [
